ListRatesOutput.example:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/">
 <soapenv:Body>
  <tns:ListRatesResponse xmlns:tns="http://www.xignite.com/services/">
   <tns:ListRatesResult>
    <tns:RateDescription><!-- between zero and unlimited repetitions of this element -->
     <tns:Outcome><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Outcome>
     <tns:Message>string</tns:Message>
     <tns:Identity>string</tns:Identity>
     <tns:Delay><!-- mandatory -->3.14</tns:Delay>
     <tns:Type><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:Type>
     <tns:Description>string</tns:Description>
     <tns:Name>string</tns:Name>
     <tns:Maturity>string</tns:Maturity>
     <tns:MaturityUnit><!-- mandatory -->string</tns:MaturityUnit>
     <tns:MaturityCount><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:MaturityCount>
     <tns:SeasonallyAdjusted><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:SeasonallyAdjusted>
     <tns:Availability>string</tns:Availability>
     <tns:Source>string</tns:Source>
     <tns:Discontinued><!-- mandatory -->true</tns:Discontinued>
     <tns:Service>string</tns:Service>
     <tns:Suffix>string</tns:Suffix>
     <tns:Factor><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Factor>
     <tns:Precision><!-- mandatory -->3</tns:Precision>
    </tns:RateDescription>
   </tns:ListRatesResult>
  </tns:ListRatesResponse>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>
